divs: Sighting DetailsSaw a giant triangle shaped craft with about 5 or 6 lights in a giant triangle shape at or around 8 pm. Slient except for helicopter trailing behind. Object apeared to be very large. Bigger than a normal blimp or bigger than anything i have ever seen in the sky. Drove to try and follow it but lights dissapeared. Called 911 and reported weird lights in the sky and the said they have had another call about the same thing that night. It was weird.
